- when we want to add event, follow these steps :

 * in HTML page

 - type form tag at HTML page
 - type fieldset tag at HTML page 
 - label the element that you want to appear to the reader/writer.
 - input the type of this elment, the id , and the placeholder
 * in JavaScript page

 - gitElementById for the form
 - add the sumbmit buttom by addEventListener
 - make a function(event)
 - remamber to preventDefault to avoid delete your data when you refresh
 -set the variable to the event by event.target.variableName.value
 -add it to the constructor or call function to make the changes . 
